data.description: Extra-large bedrooms enhance this unit. Beautifully renovated in Sept. of 2023 with new cabinets, new paint throughout the interior, new flooring downstairs and upstairs in the main areas and bedrooms. The amazing patio resurfaced by Concrete Coatings Hawaii with a transferrable lifetime warranty, just calls for outdoor relaxation. This unit is 100 sq. ft. larger than most of the units in this complex. You will have access to Mililani's 7 rec centers with pools, playgrounds, Ping-Pong tables, basketball, tennis and pickle ball courts. Enjoy the many shopping centers with multiple restaurants, shops and entertainment facilities. Mililani was named an All-American City in 1986. Great schools, parks and playgrounds all around Mililani makes this a desirable place to raise a family or retire. Schofield Barracks and Wheeler Army Airfield close by. Easy to see with less than 8 hrs. notice.
